map_editor

Class Editor

  • java.lang.Object
    • map_editor.Editor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEditor

    public class Editor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEditor
    This class initializes the map editor and asks user for options to modify the map. It also calls the loader to load map in memory. And provides user an option to verify the changes made and save the modified map to file.
    Author:
    Nikitha Papani
